---
import { withBase, cta } from '@config/site';
---

<section class="section gw" id="paths" aria-labelledby="gw-h">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Choose your path</span>
      <h2 id="gw-h" class="sec-head__q">What brought you here?</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="gw__grid">
      <article class="gw__card">
        <span class="eyebrow">Pathway A</span>
        <h3>Evaluating Ahmed for a role</h3>
        <p class="muted">
          Role fit, selected work, the full capability range, working method, evidence
          standards, and the CV.
        </p>
        <ul class="gw__list">
          <li>Where the career shift actually happened — and why it holds</li>
          <li>What Ahmed owned versus recommended versus coordinated</li>
          <li>Reasoning you can question in an interview</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn--ghost gw__go" href={withBase(cta.employer.href)}>
          {cta.employer.label} →
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="gw__card">
        <span class="eyebrow">Pathway B</span>
        <h3>Looking to improve a business</h3>
        <p class="muted">
          Common growth blockers, how the diagnosis runs, what you receive, and what it
          would cost you to find out.
        </p>
        <ul class="gw__list">
          <li>Traffic but low conversion · support volume · disorganised operations</li>
          <li>Founder dependency · new launch · new market</li>
          <li>A diagnosis before a build — often the cheapest answer wins</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn--primary gw__go" href={withBase(cta.business.href)}>
          {cta.business.label} →
        </a>
      </article>
    </div>

    <p class="faint gw__note">
      Choosing a path adjusts emphasis only. Every page stays open, indexable, and identical
      underneath — no gates, no duplicate site.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .gw__grid { display: grid; gap: var(--s5); grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  @media (max-width: 860px) { .gw__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .gw__card {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--s4);
    padding: var(--s6);
    background: var(--surface-raise);
    border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    border-radius: var(--r-lg);
    transition: border-color var(--dur-mid) var(--ease);
  }
  .gw__card:hover { border-color: var(--hairline-strong); }
  .gw__list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--s2); padding: 0; list-style: none; }
  .gw__list li {
    font-size: var(--fs-small); color: var(--text-muted);
    padding-left: var(--s4); position: relative;
  }
  .gw__list li::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0.6em;
    width: 6px; height: 1px; background: var(--teal-signal);
  }
  .gw__go { margin-top: auto; align-self: flex-start; }
  .gw__note { margin-top: var(--s5); }
</style>
